summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 64E, page 24-379 of the Seattle Municipal Code (page 156 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain property located at 976 South Harney Street from Community Business (BC) Zone to General Industrial (IG) Zone (Petition of Seattle Drug and Narcotic Center, C.F. 290022).
